## 3. Color & semantic status

Map ERP states to tokens ŌĆö do not hardcode hex colors.

| Meaning | Pattern |
|---------|---------|
| Primary action | `Button` variant `default` (`primary`) |
| Secondary / filter | `outline` or `secondary` |
| Danger / delete / failed | `destructive` variant or `text-destructive` |
| Draft / pending | `Badge variant="secondary"` + icon or text label |
| Success / posted | `text-primary` or subtle `bg-primary/10 text-primary` badge |
| Disabled nav | shadcn `disabled` on `SidebarMenuButton` ŌĆö already in `app-sidebar.tsx` |
| Charts | `--chart-1` ŌĆ” `--chart-5` from theme only |

Status badges: **icon or text + color** (e.g. "Posted", "Draft") ŌĆö WCAG requires more than hue.

