## 5. Forms & data entry

Follow patterns from `login-form.tsx`:

- Inputs: **`h-11 text-base`** on mobile-critical forms; default shadcn `Input` on dense desktop tables.
- Touch targets: minimum **44├Ś44px** ŌĆö use `h-11`, `size-10`/`size-11` icon buttons, adequate `gap` between fields.
- `inputMode` / `type`: `tel` + `inputMode="numeric"` for mobile numbers; `decimal` for weights/rates.
- Labels: `FieldLabel` + `FieldDescription` + `FieldError`; errors must be readable (`text-destructive text-sm`).
- Primary submit: full width on mobile (`w-full h-11`), inline on desktop when appropriate.
- **Keyboard:** logical tab order; Enter submits single-purpose forms; donŌĆÖt trap focus in modals without escape.

