      <tr className="text-left">
        <th className="h-10 px-3 font-medium text-muted-foreground">Party</th>
        <th className="h-10 px-3 text-right font-medium text-muted-foreground">Amount</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr className="border-b border-border transition-colors hover:bg-muted/50">
        <td className="px-3 py-2.5">ŌĆ”</td>
        <td className="px-3 py-2.5 text-right tabular-nums">ŌĆ”</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</div>
```

| Rule | Detail |
|------|--------|
| Row height | Comfortable `py-2.5`ŌĆō`py-3`; compact `py-2` only in explicitly ŌĆ£compactŌĆØ views |
| Header | `bg-muted/50`, `text-muted-foreground font-medium`, sticky header on long lists |
| Zebra | Optional `even:bg-muted/30` ŌĆö keep subtle |
| Mobile | Wrapper `overflow-x-auto`; consider **sticky first column** (`sticky left-0 z-10 bg-background`) for row identity |
| Empty | Centered message + primary action ŌĆö never a bare table |
| Loading | `Skeleton` rows matching column layout ŌĆö no spinners-only tables |

