## 12. Anti-patterns (avoid)

- Decorative fonts, excessive rounded corners on tables, or gradient text on numbers
- `opacity-50` on entire rows to mean ŌĆ£inactiveŌĆØ ŌĆö use badge or strikethrough label
- Centered multi-column numeric tables
- Multiple competing primary buttons
- Custom CSS files per feature ŌĆö use Tailwind + shadcn variants
- Europe/US-only date or currency formats in an Indian cold-storage context

When adding new routes, register titles in `routeTitles` (`app-topbar.tsx`) and nav in `app-sidebar.tsx` for consistent chrome.
